      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WHERE'S MICK (4) did a good job to finish second last time out over 390m at this track (22.52) in a Bottom Up - Maiden, the second top-three finish on the trot. Better than latest and can atone here. PAW AMARLI (2) had the drop on the lead and went on to be beaten 5.5 lengths into third (24.07) at Horsham in a Restricted WIN over 410m. Leading player again. INGA RYDER (1) copped a check in the run last time and never threatened when fifth (18.65) in a Maiden at Mt Gambier. May be worth another try. MY ANIELA (6) hit the frame here last time and looks a chance again.",
